                <p style="margin:0 0 16px;">I&#8217;m not writing to chase you. I&#8217;m writing because most homeowners who miss an appointment with us assume we&#8217;re annoyed. We&#8217;re not. The rep drove out, didn&#8217;t find you, drove back. That&#8217;s a normal part of this business. It happens.</p>

                <p style="margin:0 0 16px;">What I&#8217;d like you to know is this: the original appointment wasn&#8217;t a pitch. It was an assessment. Our team coming out to confirm what your home is actually rated for, whether it matches your zone, and whether the installed system aligns with what&#8217;s on record. About 90 minutes, on your schedule, no pressure to do anything afterward.</p>

